on of a normative question. (Statement iii is correct).\n\n**Eliminate Incorrect Answers**\n*   **B (i only):** Incorrect because ii and iii are also true.\n*   **C (i and iii):** Incorrect because ii is also true.\n*   **D (ii only):** Incorrect because i and iii are also true.\n*   **E (I don't know):** Incorrect as the answer can be derived.\n\n**Conclusion**\nAll three statements correctly classify the philosophical inquiries. Therefore, the option including all three is the correct answer.\n\nFinal Answer: ###A###"]
