t ii is true.\n\n**Eliminate Incorrect Answers**\n-   **B (i)** is incorrect because spouses living together cannot choose separate taxation.\n-   **C (i and ii)** is incorrect because statement i is false.\n-   **D (none)** is incorrect because statement ii is true.\n\n**Conclusion**\nStatement ii is the only correct statement. Therefore, Choice A is the correct answer.\n\nFinal Answer: ###A###"]
