ory limit is 6 months. Therefore, this statement is **incorrect**.\n-   **Statement ii:** The statement claims only cash contributions are allowed. Swiss law explicitly permits contributions in kind. Therefore, this statement is **incorrect**.\n-   **Statement iii:** The Act of Mediation (1803) did not found the Helvetic Republic; it marked the transition away from it. The Republic was founded in 1798. Therefore, this statement is **incorrect**.\n-   **Statement iv:** The definition provided matches the statutory definition in Art. 197 ZGB perfectly. Therefore, this statement is **correct**.\n\n**Eliminate Incorrect Answers**\n-   **B) iii and iv:** Incorrect because statement iii is false.\n-   **C) i, ii, and iii:** Incorrect because statements i, ii, and iii are all false.\n-   **D) none of the statements:** Incorrect because statement iv is true.\n\n**Conclusion**\nOnly statement iv is correct. Therefore, the correct option is A.\n\nFinal Answer: ###A###"]
